latestPosts.caption:
We often get asked—why don’t you jump on the latest design fads?
How long will your pieces stay relevant?

The answer is simple: terrazzo is timeless.

It’s crafted from natural materials—stone, glass, and cement—each carrying its own history and character.
Terrazzo has been part of design heritage for centuries, and its authenticity never fades.

Our pieces aren’t made to catch a moment’s attention,
they’re made to become part of your everyday life, growing with your space and your story.

#parmandesigns #natureinspiredfurniture #luxuryfurnituredesign #terrazzodesign #trends #terrazzoflooring #terrazzotiles #functionalfurniture #mindfulmaterials #designprocesses

Pakhru’ means bird in Marathi—a symbol of care, protection, and connection.

We brought that idea to life through terrazzo, blending natural aggregates with shimmering mother-of-pearl to create pieces full of elegance and meaning.

The swan chair represents the mother bird, graceful and nurturing.
The swan baby chair carries that tenderness forward—small, gentle, and protective.
And the swan lamp stands tall like the father—steady, guiding light in the family.

Together, these pieces tell a story of family and togetherness.

#parmandesigns #natureinspiredfurniture #luxuryfurnituredesign #terrazzodesign #birdcollection #familybird #functionalfurniture #mindfulmaterials #designprocesses

WE DON’T ALWAYS AGREE

Param and Manuj have their moments—
different opinions, clashing ideas, honest debates.

But here’s the thing:
they never let it get in the way of the work.

They listen. They push back.They figure it out together.

Because making something meaningful means trusting the process —
even when it’s messy.

That’s how Parman Designs moves forward.

#parmandesigns #natureinspiredfurniture #luxuryfurnituredesign #terrazzodesign #conflict #conflictmanagement #terrazzotiles #functionalfurniture #mindfulmaterials #designprocesses

THE STORY BEHIND PARMAN DESIGNS

Param came from a footwear background,
while Manuj grew up in the world of fashion.

They met through a mutual friend—and something just clicked.
Conversations turned into shared ideas,
and a creative partnership was born.

Parman Designs isn’t just about furniture or decor—
it’s about craftsmanship, friendship, and a vision to bring soul into every piece.

This is how our journey began, and we’re just getting started.

We are thrilled to announce that Parman Designs has won the *”Trendsetter and Futuristic Handmade Terrazzo Product Brand”* at the *Architecture and Interior Design Excellence Awards 2025!* 🏆

This award celebrates our journey of passion and dedication in creating transformative terrazzo products. A big thanks to our clients, collaborators, and everyone who pushes the boundaries of design with us. 🌟

This is just the beginning, and we look forward to more creative adventures ahead! 💫
